title: Engagement
description: Engagement refers to the student's connection to schooling.  Positive engagement is noted when students have good attendance and participate fully in school.

title: Relationships
description: "Relationships" refers to a student's connection and bond with peers and  adults.  When a student has positive relationships with teachers and staff as well as peers in school, more positive student behavior results.

title: Learning
description: Learning refers to the acquisition of knowledge and skills.
